Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.55,0:22:47.60,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\3c&H000000&\3a&H80&\bord1\blur5}ああ　跳ね上がる集中力
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.68,0:22:51.47,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\3c&H000000&\3a&H80&\bord1\blur5}たった一言で熱い
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.81,0:22:54.60,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\3c&H000000&\3a&H80&\bord1\blur5}ほんの小さな兆し
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.31,0:23:01.86,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\3c&H000000&\3a&H80&\bord1\blur5}夢見てしまう
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.69,0:23:05.95,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\3c&H000000&\3a&H80&\bord1\blur5}何でこんなに嬉しいの
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.95,0:23:09.08,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\3c&H000000&\3a&H80&\bord1\blur5}何でこんなにかなしいの
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.08,0:23:12.29,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\3c&H000000&\3a&H80&\bord1\blur5}今も隣りで眺めてる
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.29,0:23:16.71,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\3c&H000000&\3a&H80&\bord1\blur5}遠い横顔を焼きつけた
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.50,0:23:23.51,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\3c&H000000&\3a&H80&\bord1\blur5}今日はまだ届かない
